text: Mona Breckmann (born 6 September 1991) is a Faroese former footballer who played as a forward. She has been a member of the Faroe Islands women's national team. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Faroese women's footballers Category:People from Tórshavn Category:Faroe Islands women's international footballers
